


 Playing around with the Sniper problem in Growing object oriented applicatins with TESTs

Problem
  A fictionary AuctionHouse conducts online Auctions. Clients may bid for items.
  Each auction is unique and is determined by the identity of the item it is selling

  Construct a client UI to represent auctions, auction status reporting etc
  It should also be possible to AutoBid an item till a specified stop price


Tasks
 1. Join the auction process, do nothing
 2. Join and listen to bids
 3. Join and bid some item and loose the bid
 4. Join, Bid and Win
 5. Join, AutoBid and loose
 6. Join, AutoBid and Win

